Package: redis-fractalsql
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libc6 (>= 2.38),
 redis-server
Description: Stochastic Fractal Search module for Redis
 redis-fractalsql is a native C module for Redis 6.2 / 7.0 / 7.2 /
 7.4 (ABI-compatible with 8.x) that exposes a FRACTAL.SEARCH command
 backed by a LuaJIT-compiled Stochastic Fractal Search optimizer.
 The command is flagged readonly / fast / allow-stale. LuaJIT is
 statically linked into the module; the only runtime dependency is
 glibc.
 .
 After installation, enable the module by adding the following line
 to redis.conf (the post-install script prints this):
 .
     loadmodule /usr/lib/redis/modules/fractalsql.so
 .
 An example config snippet is installed at
 /etc/redis/modules-available/fractalsql.conf.
